name: I know my great-great-grandfather by his clippings
description:
I thank and I know my great-great-grandfather Casimiro Barbosa Ferreira de Carvalho by his newspaper clippings. He had a fabric market in the centre of Rio de Janeiro and he liked beach fashion for sure. 

Photography: Woman at Copacabana beach in the beggining of the XX century.
